--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Description: Display an area chart of execution history of a given job by step
-- Revision History:
-- ---Date--- ---Programmer---- ---Description----------------------------------
-- 2011-11-08 Katrin Zanevsky	Original public version.
-- 2011-12-06 Andrew Zanevsky	Disregard old partially purged executions.
